Are you getting the full story? Go to https://ground.news/KiN to access world-wide sources and compare coverage. Subscribe for 40% off unlimited access.

Support us by becoming a Patron and get access to exclusive content: https://kgs.link/patreon

Sources & further reading:
https://sites.google.com/view/meat-torture/

Most of us love animals but also eat meat. Unfortunately, most animals we eat live in truly horrible conditions. We dont torture them for better meat, just for cheaper meat. If we all paid just a bit more, we could avoid most animal suffering  often just for a few cents per meal. What would it truly cost us to avoid animal torture and still eat meat?
